If it is only a prefix that is missing and that prefix is not used, then I believe it is not incorrect.  Something to try might be:

declare option xdmp:output "undeclareprefixes = no" ;

Note that this will not work in cq or Query Console.

Correction:

declare option xdmp:output "undeclare-prefixes = no" ; 

Also, you can set this on the app server with the output undeclare prefixes option.
